{"tid":1402124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［完美辯護］藍絲親戚質問有人丟氣油彈wor仲橕？","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:08:15.000Z","uid":275189,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6e438d146ea417357fa1f0377e4c370a07b823","tid":1402124,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"駁完無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n範例：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">由69和平示威發展至此！心痛莫名！暴力無人願見，痛心是林鄭政權不肯與民同行，非要與民為敵，民怨暴發，引來今時今日局面。如今能緩解政治問題的，只有政治方法，望一眾和理非緊抱信念，85罷工罷市，迫使政府作出交待，好讓香港回復和平安定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原理：<br />\n（1）善用連藍絲都不能反對的論點: 不要暴力、希望社會安定<br />\n（2）說明69很和平，引證暴力是政權迫使的<br />\n（3）轉移焦點，聚焦於政權暴政<br />\n（4）合理化85罷工，繼續宣傳<br />\n（5）用較書面用語，老一輩比較受落<br />\n<br />\n個group 即刻dead air到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff07b2baa4d3ac70690adc49b6ffc278c669be38","tid":1402124,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"85"},{"pid":"6b0d684efdbe973ecd710f370ba94292332b871a","tid":1402124,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"罷"},{"pid":"63ae7acfda4add185ea2290577a5a3de802d196f","tid":1402124,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"工"},{"pid":"8339105ed9daf9d19da5a09e1321e791f346cfdd","tid":1402124,"uid":275189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"500ddabf3d9df32900cf73fd1ecbdcfdaca8cb54","tid":1402124,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"人地拎自已前途企上前線<br />\n你可以唔支持/唔理解佢地既做法<br />\n但唔該俾番D尊重 語氣唔該溫和少少 <br />\n除左佢地老豆老母無人有資格鬧佢地<br />\n<br />\n大家咪俾D低級打手帶風向 口臭撚見一個BLOCK一個就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426e1b59204f7fb3af1760385